examples.en: Later the Indians fought the Anglo settlers.
Many of the Indians have become acculturated.
The Sioux Indians placed a high value on generosity.
Outside, the children were playing cowboys and Indians.
I'm usually pulling for the Indians instead of the cowboys.
A pendant of white nephrite jade is often worn by Indians as a talisman to ward off heart disease.
The Indians have extended the hand of friendship (=shown that they want to be friends with another country).
